        q: "Can I get lip filler if I have a history of cold sores?",
        a: "Yes, with antiviral prophylaxis. Injection procedures can trigger HSV reactivation in patients with oral herpes. An antiviral medication (typically valacyclovir) is prescribed before any lip procedure for patients with this history."
