    metaTitle: "Your TSH Is Normal — But Your Thyroid May Not Be Fine | Revitalize",
    description: "Why normal TSH does not mean optimal thyroid function — a clinical explanation of the full thyroid picture, what the reference range misses, and what a complete thyroid evaluation looks like.",
